column10:
My rating: 75 / 100.
(+) Good 90-ties 'Theme Hospital' successor;
(+) Cartoonish graphics add something fun to the game;
(+) Humorous representation of diseases / room equipment;
(+) Game mechanics are introduced little by little in campaign;
(+) The game difficulty should be accurate for everyone;
(–) No chance to play with / adjust rooms design;
(–) Sometimes gameplay is too monotonous.
